data.meta_description: Pauline Koch was born on February  8, 1858 in Stuttgart, daughter of Julius Judas Rudolf Dorzbacher Koch and Jette Bernheimer. She was married on August  8, 1876 in Cannstatt, Württemberg, Germany to Hermann Einstein, they gave birth to 1 child. She died on February 20, 1920 in Berlin, Berlin West, Germany. This information is part of Family tree Rosen by Frank Rosen on Genealogy Online.
